{"tid":2973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【興航解散】停飛第5日 59名乘客滯留中國","createTime":"2016-11-26T04:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T04:09:47.000Z","uid":6038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9067afd71f411d55cf2ebab5db330fd5b0623107","tid":2973,"uid":6038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T04:09:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161126&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=55967702\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161126%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D55967702&d=9H99dlmJ%2Bs6KO3W%2FO%2Bp%2B8sW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=c0223bb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161126%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D55967702&h=8aae8025\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161126&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=55967702</a><br />\n<br />\n【興航解散】停飛第5日 59名乘客滯留中國<br />\n<br />\n復興航空本月22日突然停飛，10萬人次受影響，其中約萬人被滯留海外陸續透過其他航空公司航班返台。根據台觀光局統計，國際線今天起將無旅行社滯留海外，兩岸線今、明2天仍有59人得轉其他航空公司航班返台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}